text: Gaziza Abdinabiyeva (Газиза Абдинабиева; 3 January 1948 – 18 April 2021) was a Soviet and later Kazakhstani stage actress. She was awarded several orders including the Order of Kurmet and Order of Parasat. Abdinabiyeva died on 18 April 2021, aged 73. ==References== Category:Kazakhstani people Category:1948 births Category:Stage actors Category:2021 deaths
